Sentencas: A typical Ce0.85Gd0.15O2-delta (CDC15) composition of CeO2-Gd2O3 system is synthesized by modified sol - gel technique known as citrate-complexation.
Titulo: Citrate-complexation synthesized Ce0.85Gd0.15O2-δ (GDC15) as solid electrolyte for intermediate temperature SOFC

Sentencas: TG-DTA, XRD, FT-IR, Raman, FE-SEM/EDX and ac impedance analysis are carried out for structural and electrical characterization.
Titulo: Citrate-complexation synthesized Ce0.85Gd0.15O2-δ (GDC15) as solid electrolyte for intermediate temperature SOFC

Sentencas: XRD pattern confirmed the well crystalline cubic fluorite structure of CDC15 after calcining at 873 K. Raman spectral bands at 463, 550 and 600 cm(-1) are also in agreement with these structural features.
Titulo: Citrate-complexation synthesized Ce0.85Gd0.15O2-δ (GDC15) as solid electrolyte for intermediate temperature SOFC

Sentencas: FE-SEM image shows well-defined grains separated from grain boundary and good densification.
Titulo: Citrate-complexation synthesized Ce0.85Gd0.15O2-δ (GDC15) as solid electrolyte for intermediate temperature SOFC

Sentencas: Ac impedance studies reveal that GDC15 has oxide ionic conductivity similar to that reported for Ce0.9Gd0.1O2-delta (GDC10) and Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-delta (GDC20).
Titulo: Citrate-complexation synthesized Ce0.85Gd0.15O2-δ (GDC15) as solid electrolyte for intermediate temperature SOFC

Sentencas: Ionic and electronic transference numbers at 673 K are found to be 0.95 and 0.05, respectively.
Titulo: Citrate-complexation synthesized Ce0.85Gd0.15O2-δ (GDC15) as solid electrolyte for intermediate temperature SOFC

Sentencas: This indicates the possible application of GDC15 as a potential electrolyte for IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: Citrate-complexation synthesized Ce0.85Gd0.15O2-δ (GDC15) as solid electrolyte for intermediate temperature SOFC
